<L>In loo&s;e inglorious luxury. With him</L>
<L>His friend, the <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">ALCERMON SIDNEY.</NOTE> BRITISH CASSIUS, fearle&s;s bled;</L>
<L>Of high determin'd &s;pirit, roughly brave,<MILESTONE N="1521"></L>
<L>By antient learning to th' enlighten'd love</L>
