<L>In awful <HI>Sages</HI> and in noble <HI>Bards</HI>;</L>
<L>Soon as the light of dawning &s;cience &s;pread <MILESTONE N="1525"></L>
<L>Her orient ray, and wak'd the Mu&s;es' &s;ong.</L>
<L>Thine is a BACON; haple&s;s in his choice,</L>
