<L>Kind Nature form'd, deep, comprehen&s;ive, clear,</L>
<L>Exact, and elegant; in one rich &s;oul,</L>
<L>PLATO, the STAGYRITE, and TULLY join'd.</L>
<L>The great deliverer he! who from the gloom <MILESTONE N="1535"></L>
