<L>Daughter of HEAVEN! that, &s;low-a&s;cending &s;till,<MILESTONE N="1540"></L>
<L>Inve&s;tigating &s;ure the chain of things,</L>
<L>With radiant finger points to HEAVEN again.</L>
<L><PB N="93" REF="021495_0105_0FB404BF503C47D0">The generous <NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot">ANTHONY ASHLEY COOPER, Earl of <HI>Shafte&s;bury.</HI></NOTE> ASHLEY thine, the friend of Man;</L>
<L>Who &s;cann'd his Nature with a brother's eye,</L>
