<L>Baffling, <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">as</NOTE> like thy hoar cliffs the loud &s;ea-wave.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>O THOU! by who&s;e almighty <HI>Nod</HI> the &s;cale</L>
