</LG>
<LG>
<L>AMONG the crooked lanes on every hedge,</L>
<L>The glow-worm lights his gem; and, thro' the dark,</L>
<L>A moving radiance twinkles. <HI>Evening</HI> yields <MILESTONE N="1676"></L>
