<L>Or in the wint'ry glebe whatever lies <MILESTONE N="1261"></L>
<L>Conceal'd, and fatte<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">s with the riche&s;t &s;ap:</L>
<L>The&s;e are not wanting: nor the milky drove,</L>
<L>Luxuriant, &s;pread o'er all the lowing vale;</L>
<L>Nor bleating mountains; nor the chide of &s;treams,</L>
