<L>To Nature's voice attends, from month to month,</L>
<L><PB N="143" REF="021495_0156_0FB4050C91CE4DC8">And day to day, thro' the revolving year; <MILESTONE N="1305"></L>
<L>Admiring &s;ees her in her every &s;hape,</L>
